title: 11/04/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 11/04/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On today's Dan Patrick Show, DP Talks to Tom Silverstein of the Milwaukee Journal Sentinel about what went down with Aaron Rodgers yesterday. Ross Tucker tells us which story line he thinks would be better, Jordan Love playing well or poorly? And Browns Mary Kay Cabot explains what the future for OBJ in Cleveland may look like.
